sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics<br/>6060/TCP healthz
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant Exec as argoexec sidecar
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Artifact Store<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: POST Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event: new Workflow<br/>Informer stream
    WFC->>WFC: Reconcile workflow steps<br/>MAX_OPERATION_TIME: 30s
    WFC->>K8s: Create execution Pod<br/>with argoexec sidecar<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled & started

    activate Exec
    Exec->>Exec: Execute step command<br/>(emissary mode)
    Exec->>S3: Upload step artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / AccessKey
    S3-->>Exec: Upload confirmed
    Exec->>K8s: Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>Auth: Workflow SA Token
    deactivate Exec

    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event: TaskResult created
    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 2: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    WFC->>WFC: CronWorkflow workers (8)<br/>check schedule
    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow from CronWorkflow<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Note right of WFC: Follows Flow 1 above

    Note over DSP,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection

    WFC->>K8s: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>S3: Delete expired artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / AccessKey
    S3-->>WFC: Deletion confirmed
    WFC->>K8s: Update ArtifactGCTask status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
